## Important Notes

**Legal & Ethical Considerations:**
- Always obtain proper authorization before scanning networks
- Respect privacy and data protection laws
- Use tools responsibly and only on networks you own or have permission to test
- Many scanning tools can be detected by IDS/IPS systems

**Best Practices:**
- Start with non-intrusive tools (ping, traceroute)
- Document your findings
- Keep tools updated
- Understand what each tool does before using it
- Practice in isolated lab environments first

**Platform Availability:**
- Most tools are available on Linux/Unix systems
- Windows has native alternatives or downloadable versions
- macOS supports most Unix-based tools natively

